{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Settler's Domain demo has all the core mechanics present in the full game, but with less structures and resources and in a limited time frame. The demo is meant give players a basic understanding of what Settler's Domain is, and what the start of a new world feels like. The demo offers an accelerated year of play, so players can see all four seasons. In the demo, each season is 10 days, instead of the normal 30 days.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The following mechanics are all present in the demo:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/gatherHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources to build new structures and keep your settlers alive. Resource management is essential for a thriving settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/gatherGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/buildHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add new structures! There are 5 main types: housing, production, exploration, services, and processing. Placement is key for survival- can you maximize efficiency and still keep your settlement looking pretty?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/buildGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/exploreHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear away the unknown to discover more resources and fresh landscapes in a limitless procedural world that grows with your settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/exploreGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/recruitHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Influence to recruit new settlers to your cause. Larger populations can produce more resources, but need more food and housing to survive!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/recruitGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Note: Settler's Domain is still early in development, and this page is likely to change often in the coming months.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3501740?t=1739550988","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3501740?t=1739550988","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/dcfa740d484c8921e82f759a902b0415cf05aed9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739550988","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/dcfa740d484c8921e82f759a902b0415cf05aed9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739550988","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Settler's Domain demo has all the core mechanics present in the full game, but with less structures and resources and in a limited time frame. The demo is meant give players a basic understanding of what Settler's Domain is, and what the start of a new world feels like. The demo offers an accelerated year of play, so players can see all four seasons. In the demo, each season is 10 days, instead of the normal 30 days.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The following mechanics are all present in the demo:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/gatherHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources to build new structures and keep your settlers alive. Resource management is essential for a thriving settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/gatherGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/buildHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add new structures! There are 5 main types: housing, production, exploration, services, and processing. Placement is key for survival- can you maximize efficiency and still keep your settlement looking pretty?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/buildGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/exploreHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear away the unknown to discover more resources and fresh landscapes in a limitless procedural world that grows with your settlement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/exploreGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/recruitHeader.png?t=1739550988\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Influence to recruit new settlers to your cause. Larger populations can produce more resources, but need more food and housing to survive!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/extras/recruitGif.gif?t=1739550988\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Note: Settler's Domain is still early in development, and this page is likely to change often in the coming months.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["rick"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3396920","name":"Settler's Domain"},"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501740/header.jpg?t=1739550988","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257093494,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257093494/movie480.mp4?t=1739469660","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257093494/movie_max.mp4?t=1739469660"},"name":"Pre-Alpha Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257093494/b716b281d3aab46c25f83b51fa8b04f748357561/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739469660","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257093494/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739469660","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257093494/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739469660"}}],"name":"Settler's Domain Demo","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> x86_64 with SSE4.2 or ARMv8 - Intel Core i5-6600K, AMD Ryzen 5 1600, Snapdragon X Elite<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Vulkan 1.2 - NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050 (Pascal), AMD Radeon RX 460 (GCN 4.0)<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong>